    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Locks designed with a push button or a turn-locking outside knob. When so locked, there is no entrance by key from the outside.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
